# HTML
<ul>
"/" - First - (root)- GET
"/login"-splash -(login page)- GET
"/search" - search page(latest 5 results) - GET
"/display"- display and edit page(frozen to editable property) - GET
</ul>
# API
POST "/api/login"- login operation: POST "/api/login"- sends id
POST "/api/users"- create new newUser - POST  "/api/users"- send id
GET "/api/logout/:id"- log out - GET
GET "/api/users/:id"
"/api/newthought/:id + body" - create new thought -> search page  -POST
"/api/search/:id + other params"- search from search page - GET
"/api/display/:id" - return one displayed thought - GET
"/api/edit/:id   +body"- to update Thoughts, redirect to / POST-PUT



